A mouse called Ventus X has a built-in honeycomb grill to let the skin breathe and a rugged coating so sweaty gamers can continue to use it . 
  The mouse provides ‘enhanced modern technology and classic design that fits all gamers and bring style to gaming’ It has a matte coating or rough texture and rubber grips down its side . 
